Description: You have complete control over atomic particles and waves, and can use them to disable and weaken your enemies, as well as boost your own power. Many of your powers have the ability to surround your targets with negatrons or positrons. Should you combine both of these in a single target, it will result in Electron-Positron annihilation producing a burst of Gamma Rays which will inflict a small amount of damage, and in addition debuff the target's damage output and accuracy. Enemies also have a small chance of being stunned or confused.

Powers.DescLong: A focused attack of intense sonic power that violently sends a nearby foe flying. Deals minimal damage, but can be very effective. Recharge: Fast

Powers.DescShort: Melee, Moderate DMG(Smashing/Energy), chance for Hold
Powers.DescLong: Strident Echo deals minor damage over time. It has a low chance of causing a migraine, leaving the target shaking in pain and helpless. Recharge: Slow
Encases the target in an field of sonic waves, dealing energy damage and holding them in place. Recharge: Slow

Greatly boosts your attacks for a few seconds. Slightly increases chance to hit. Moderately increases the duration of mez effects. Moderately increases the chance for Sound Manipulation powers to induce Migraines. Recharge: Long

Powers.DescShort: Melee (AoE), High DMG(Sonic/Energy), chance for Hold
Powers.DescLong: You create a large field of sonic waves, causing damage to all foes around you. It has a moderate chance of causing migraines, leaving them shaking in pain and helpless. Recharge: Slow
Creates a barrier around the caster which reduces incoming energy and smashing damage while granting absorption. Recovery is also increased. Recharge: Moderate
You set up a constant wave of sonic energy around yourself, weakening the Damage Resistance of all nearby foes. Recharge: Moderate
You generate a powerful sonic wave that will knock back and disorient foes in front of you for a short time. Recharge: Long

Powers.DescShort: Melee, Heavy DMG(Smashing/Energy), chance for Hold
Powers.DescLong: You generate an Earsplitting sound wave right in the face of your foe, inflicting great damge. It has a good chance of causing severe headache leaving them shaking in pain and helpless. Damage: Heavy, Recharge: Slow
